GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_StrategyOverview> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_StrategyOverview> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StrategyOverview> ;
    narr:childCount "51"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers aswritten.ai's strategy across fundraising, go-to-market, pricing, product positioning, and founding philosophy. The fundraising thread moves most: from [splitting the F&F brief from the seed raise](narr:Narrative_FFvsSeedSplit) (Mar 15) into [three documents](narr:Narrative_ThreeDocFundraisingSplit) and [two parallel incubator/SAFE paths](narr:Narrative_DualFundingPaths) (Mar 20), to a [SEAL/shared-earnings instrument](narr:Narrative_SEALFunding) (Mar 30–31) and the [one-round-ever thesis](narr:Narrative_OneRoundEver) (Apr 5), resolving May 17–18 into a [two-tranche envelope](narr:Claim_TwoTrancheRaiseEnvelope) and sharpening May 27 into a [bridge-to-milestone structure](narr:Narrative_TwoTrancheRaiseStructure) governed by [calibrated growth discipline](narr:Narrative_CalibratedGrowthDiscipline). Go-to-market spans [beta-as-full-consulting](narr:Narrative_BetaAsConsulting), the [the enterprise customer PE-backed enterprise archetype](narr:Narrative_EnterpriseCustomerShapeArchetypeConverting), [SMS-first acquisition](narr:Positioning_SMSProduct), and [perspective-on-spec outreach](narr:Narrative_PerspectiveOnSpec). Positioning holds [venture-scale ambition on calm-company execution](narr:Narrative_VentureScaleCalmCompanyExecution), a [shared-backend moat](narr:Moat_SharedBackend), and a [career through-line](narr:Narrative_ThroughLine) from physics to organizational memory. The [YC application](narr:Narrative_WhyYC) and [demo structure](narr:Decision_YCDemoBeats) sit alongside.""" ;
